text:
Thank you everyone who participated in the theme challenge! It was an awesome experience. Hope you all had fun.

Whether you won or not, remember your theme is out there on the marketplace. You can keep improving your theme, it’s listing, and it’s documentation making it better for customers and making it stand out from the competition.

We’ve already heard reports from participants they’ve had some sales, and new clients for ongoing work come out of it.
Congratulations to <@UFYT8A030> great work on your theme.
<@U54TVT3C1> Thank you very much, all the projects are wonderful!
